        <p>This Online Privacy Policy ("Privacy Policy") provides Visitors and Users of Contentwriters.com (collectively, "You") with important information regarding ContentWriters' collection, storage and use of personally identifiable information.</p>

    <p>This Privacy Policy applies only to personally identifiable information collected on the website(s) operated by ContentWriters on which this Privacy Policy is posted (collectively, "Website"), and does not apply to any other information collected by ContentWriters offline or through any other means.</p>

