    <h3>Requests for Registration Information</h3>

    <p>ContentWriters collects personally identifiable information from Users only when Users voluntarily provide it as part of the registration process ("Registration Information") to open an Account. ContentWriters never automatically collects any information that specifically identifies Users, such as their name, address, or e-mail address. </p>

    <p>It is the User's choice whether or not to provide Registration Information to ContentWriters, but such information is required in order for ContentWriters to provide you with services - namely, access to and/or participation in Assignments, to post Assignments and receive Writer Services, and certain other features of the Website. </p>

